final_preprocessed_data_augmentation.py：use the 30% anomaly fixed dataset for data augmentation and increase the data to 35040
final_preprocessed_data_augmentation_100k.py:use the 30% anomaly 35040 dataset for data augmentation and increase the data to 100k

100k_data_preparation_x_windows_formed.py： form the x_windows of 100k dataset for model training
data_preparation_x_windows_formed.py:form the x_windows of 35040 dataset for model training
